1. Install kafka_2.12-2.4.0, Python 3

2. Install Python module confluent-kafka, kafka-python

3. Start the server:(from kafka_2.12-2.4.0 binaries)
	bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties &
	bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties & 

4. Get inside src directory

5. Copy mock_data.json to src/

6. python kafka-producer.py

7. python kafka-consumer.py